# Tom Collins

> Gin and sparkling lemonade. #cocktail #gin

- Gin | 2 oz | 
- Simple Syrup | 3/4 oz | 
- Lemon | 3/4 oz | Juiced

Shake the gin, simple syrup, and lemon juice with ice.

Strain into a Collins glass filled with ice.

- Soda | Club | 

Top with club soda. Add a straw if you have one on hand.
